asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

description: Hello fellow flufs and an extra special hello to the lady flufs out there.Im Hugh Flufner, welcome to my island. Well, Fluf island, as I like to call it.I love to throw amazing parties out here, sun drenched coasts, forests, carrots, mycelium, all the good stuff.Actually, a little secret,I have a mycelium IV connector in my ear,keeps me young and full of drive.Nobody likes to lose their drive, and that is the beauty of the metaverse.Anyway, a little more about me as I am sure you want to know, I am a pretty fashionable kind of fluf, very generous, and can afford to be, as my magazine company, Flufboy, has made me a lot of money. Quite ironic that I carried on the playboy bunny theme for my magazine here as well. I also find it funny that the lady flufs dont even need to get dressed up in their bunny outfits now, which saves so much time and effort Since moving to fluf world, I have made a segway into the VR side of things I can take you to my movie studio to have a go if you like. It is VERY realistic Technology is advancing very fast in that area, Otherwise, I spend most of my days sipping on mycelium cocktails, chewing on delicious carrots, and mixing with my other wonderful non judgemental fluf friends I look forward to spending time with you in the metaverse, it is growing fast.

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.
